src:
Live Streaming Manchester United vs Partizan Belgrade di Vidio
07 Nov 2019, 22:30 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Manchester United (MU) bisa memastikan kelolosan ke babak 32 besar Liga Europa musim ini. Untuk itu, MU perlu mengalahkan Partizan Belgrade di kandang sendiri nanti.
MU akan menjamu Partizan Belgrade di Old Trafford pada matchday 4 Grup L Liga Europa 2019/20, Jumat (8/11/2019).
Pada matchday sebelumnya, MU menang 1-0 di markas Partizan. Pasukan Ole Gunnar Solskjaer pulang dari Serbia berkat gol penalti Anthony Martial.
MU memimpin klasemen sementara Grup L dengan 7 poin, unggul atas AZ Alkmaar (5), Partizan (4), dan Astana (0).
Kemenangan atas Partizan di Old Trafford akan menjamin kelolosan MU ke babak 32 besar dengan dua laga terssisa. Red Devils tentu tak ingin menyia-nyiakannya.
Namun, MU tetap harus waspada. Pasalnya, Partizan sedang bersemangat usai menang telak 4-0 atas Vojvodina di liga utama Serbia. Partizan memenangi laga tersebut lewat gol-gol Bibras Nacho (2), Umar Sadiq, dan Sasa Zdjelar.
Untuk mengatasi Partizan, MU perlu melakukan beberapa pembenahan, terutama dalam hal merancang peluang dan penyelesaian akhir. Yang jelas, mereka harus tampil jauh lebih baik daripada ketika ditekuk tuan rumah Bournemouth 0-1 di Premier League akhir pekan kemarin.

Saksikan Live Streaming Manchester United vs Partizan Belgrade di bawah ini.
text:
Live Streaming of Manchester United vs Partizan Belgrade in Vidio
Nov 7 2019, 22:30 by Bola.net
Soccer - Manchester United (MU) can ensure a breakthrough into the last 32 of the Europa League this season. For that, MU needs to defeat Partizan Belgrade at home later.
MU will host Partizan Belgrade at Old Trafford on Matchday 4 Group L Europa League 2019/20, Friday (11/08/2019).
On the previous matchday, Manchester United won 1-0 at Partizan headquarters. Ole Gunnar Solskjaer's men returned from Serbia thanks to Anthony Martial's penalty.
MU leads the standings of Group L with 7 points, ahead of AZ Alkmaar (5), Partizan (4) and Astana (0).
Victory over Partizan at Old Trafford will guarantee a breakthrough MU into the last 32 with two remaining matches. Red Devils certainly do not want to waste it.
However, MU still must be vigilant. Because, Partizan was excited after a 4-0 win over Vojvodina in the Serbian premier league. Partizan won the match with goals from Bibras Nacho (2), Umar Sadiq and Sasa Zdjelar.
To overcome Partizan, MU needs to make some improvements, especially in terms of designing opportunities and the final solution. What is clear, they must perform much better than when bent host Bournemouth 0-1 in the Premier League last weekend.

Watch Live Streaming Manchester United vs Partizan Belgrade below.
